  skills/diataxis-doc-system/SKILL.md — Router + quality gate
  skills/diataxis-doc-system/references/ — 5 rule files

New agents:
  agents/doc-writer-tutorial.md   — Golden path, checkpoints
  agents/doc-writer-howto.md      — Problem-focused, flexibility
  agents/doc-writer-explain.md    — Design Doc, ADR, 4+1 View (opus)
  agents/doc-writer-reference.md  — Tables-first, code sync

New command:
  commands/write-doc.md — /write-doc entry point
